  <section class="main-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
      	<div class="col-md-12">
    			<div class="row">
          	<div class="col-md-12">
        			<div class="text-block animated-content fade_in animate"> <span style="color: #bbbbbb; font-size: 12px;">This giveaway may be discontinued at any time without notice. At any time and without prior notice, Ripple Labs may change the total XRP given away per day, as well as the WCG point to XRP giveaway ratio. Ripple Labs is not affiliated with or endorsed by World Community Grid, nor do we endorse them. Please report bugs and direct questions about this giveaway to support@ripple.com. Otherwise, please refer to support from WCG for particulars about running their client. Security bugs, in this giveaway, must be reported unused to be eligible for the Ripple XRP Bug Bounty. Please report security bugs in accordance with the bounty rules. If you find a security bug in World Community Grid, please inform them directly as we have no special access to their team.</span>
        			</div>
          	</div>
          </div>
      	</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

